lastfm.summary: "Harvest Sky" is a song by French musician Oklou and American musician Underscores, from the former's debut studio album, Choke Enough (2025). It was released on October 16, 2024, through True Panther Sounds, as a double single with the song "Obvious". Compositionally, "Harvest Sky" has been described as combining "traditional folk melodies" with "clubby" soundscapes. It starts off with a "trance melody", which builds as the song becomes a "big room anthem". Read more on Last.fm.
